reentrancy-3 vulnerable.description:
InsecureEtherVault.withdraw() (examples/reentrancy-3/vulnerable/contract.sol#15-21) can divide by zero:
	- extra = 55 / zero (examples/reentrancy-3/vulnerable/contract.sol#17)

arithmetic-1 vulnerable.description:
InsecureEtherVault.deposit() (examples/arithmetic-1/vulnerable/contract.sol#10-32) can divide by zero:
	- f = 2 / e (examples/arithmetic-1/vulnerable/contract.sol#13)

InsecureEtherVault.deposit() (examples/arithmetic-1/vulnerable/contract.sol#10-32) can divide by zero:
	- e = ko / myval (examples/arithmetic-1/vulnerable/contract.sol#22)

InsecureEtherVault.getEtherBalance() (examples/arithmetic-1/vulnerable/contract.sol#48-54) can divide by zero:
	- raiseserror = 2 / anotherzero (examples/arithmetic-1/vulnerable/contract.sol#51)

manilla vulnerable.description:

	- currentAllowance = currentAllowance / test (examples/manilla/vulnerable/contract.sol#311)
